Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The base chart layer in packages/charts is ported from Zentry's zTerminal
(zentry-nexus) charting components.

This project depends on, and (in the CLI scaffold and B1 packages) may
redistribute, the following third-party software under their respective
licenses:

  - liveline (npm: liveline@0.0.7) — live price-chart engine; vendored with a
    local patch for retina rendering and axis-label precision
    (see patches/liveline@0.0.7.patch).
  - d3, d3-hierarchy — chart math and layout.
  - unicornstudio-react — optional animated background (host-only; loaded
    lazily from a CDN).
  - react, react-dom — peer dependencies provided by the host app.

Each retains its own copyright and license; consult the respective package for
details.
